--------------------------------------------------------------
JON THURLOW DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 4 releases...

 * 2006 - A Life Thats Worthy

 * 2012 - Heat Of Your Gaze

Jon Thurlow is an intercessory missionary at the International House of Prayer (IHOP) in Kansas City, Missouri, where he regularly leads worship in the prayer room.

Be Blessed,
